## 7. XlsWorkbook — Excel Export

```rust
let page = XlsPage::new("orders")
    .add_block(XlsBlock::new("orders", 0, 0, "Order Report").span(3, 1));
let workbook = XlsWorkbook::new().add_page(page);
let json = workbook.to_json_value();
```

